  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of three concentrations of a
      development drug compared to ointment base (vehicle) in subjects with Atopic Dermatitis (AD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
